### 4. [Portfolio Analytics Workflow](mdc:.cursor/rules/portfolio-analytics-workflow.mdc)
**Purpose**: Comprehensive performance measurement and attribution
**Key Components**: PerformanceCalculator, AttributionAnalyzer, RiskAnalyzer, ReportGenerator
